gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

They came to my house, two brothers together; there was no idol in the temple at home;
After that, news spread in the village; there's no one who has come to my place.

Here are the two couplets translated:

He has arrived, is staying in Rajni's home, with Hari in his heart's hope; 
He will not jump at Zankhana's weight, whenever he will scrutinize Shyam's prosperity.
